CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 30, 1955, pg. 1 reads: "The Alphas' Cabarama - A happy throng enjoyed the Alpha Phi Alpha's Cabarama last Friday night at the Royal Ballroom. Pictured are some of the tables filled with revelers who enjoyed the affair. - Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Women and men dancing, with others seated at banquet tables, in the Royal Ballroom for Alpha Phi Alpha Cabarama event
